<ul id="topics">
<li><img alt="" src="../images/down.gif"> <a href="#requests">Algorithme d'attribution des requ&ecirc;tes</a></li>
</ul><h3 class="directives">Directives</h3>
<p>Ce module ne fournit aucune directive.</p>
